      joins affected_stop_ids to station_feeder_routes, emits one cascade alert
      per feeder route to ripple-alerts; WARNs visibly on non-subway alerts
    - inject_alert.py defaults now use real station ids (Bloor-Yonge 99999,
      St George 99972) so the demo cascades end to end
    - Makefile: logs-ripple, kafka-read-ripple
    
